text.tspan: Manuel is a highly educated developer and animator from Portugal. He has
been around Europe working for several well-renomed gaming studios
before he finally made his way to Sweden. He has been offered by his
employer to learn the language in order to acclimatize better in his new
environment.

text.tspan: 1. One of Manuel's problems is that he is juggling the new job, acclimatizing
to a new Life in a new country while trying to find the time to learn the
language. He often finds himself in a situation where he prioritize giving
work some extra hours in order to impress his new boss.
2. Manuel finds it difficult to find time for the Swedish classes and he is
starting to fall behind. His confidence is taking a turn by his absence and
lack of consistency.

text.data-name: Manuel wants his Swedish learning to go as smooth as possible. If he could throw money at the language learning in order to solve it, he would. He wants to see fast progress with little amount of effort. He also wants to save as much time and effort as pos
text.tspan: Manuel wants his Swedish learning to go as smooth as possible. If he could
throw money at the language learning in order to solve it, he would. He
wants to see fast progress with little amount of effort. He also wants to save
as much time and effort as possible when it comes to finding the information
himself. Worst case scenario would be to have to google for answers
yourself.
